      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014not a single scratch or smudge anywhere. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new car feel. I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
