    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is mechanically impeccable, with proactive rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement already completed. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile engagement, sending power through a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis maintains its original suspension geometry and factory-spec forged wheels, while the interior displays zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. A truly turn-key enthusiast vehicle with a comprehensive service dossier and zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
